item.title: Cyber Apocalypse 2021
item.description: Cyber Apocalypse 2021 I came into this one pretty out of practice. I haven’t spent much time on the pentesting front since I started studying for my CCNA a few months back. I still had a lot of fun with it and will definitely be participating next year.
